race.comment: PASIMA (2) returned in style when narrowly prevailing over this track and trip. Has never missing the frame second-up, and looks primed to go back-to-back. ZOU BIG BOY (3) resumes after a strong previous campaign that included a hat-trick of wins. With two trials under his belt, he should be forward enough to make an immediate impact. BLACK MINTO (5) was below market expectations last time but still boxed on well for third on the Poly, following a win there prior. His best figures stack up and he's worth forgiving. GIDDAY GIDDAY (6) improved sharply last start when narrowly beaten at Toowoomba and looks capable of progressing further.
